  <name>Radian</name>
  <summary>Match gaming sensitivity across different games</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Radian helps gamers calibrate and match their mouse sensitivity across different games.
      It measures the raw mouse counts needed for a complete 360-degree rotation,
      allowing you to maintain consistent aim across any game.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Test 360-degree rotations with a single keypress</li>
      <li>Fine-tune sensitivity with keyboard shortcuts while gaming</li>
      <li>Save and manage multiple sensitivity profiles</li>
      <li>Background operation with customizable hotkeys</li>
      <li>Minimal resource usage</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
